# Graphite Color Token System

## Rule: No hardcoded colors

Every color value in `src/` **must** come from the theme via `useTheme()`. Raw hex strings are forbidden in component and screen files.

```typescript
// BAD — hardcoded hex
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  card: { backgroundColor: "#141414", borderColor: "#2E2E2E" },
  label: { color: "#B0B0B0" },
});

// GOOD — theme tokens
const theme = useTheme();
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  card: { backgroundColor: theme.colors.depth.level1, borderColor: theme.colors.border.level1 },
  label: { color: theme.colors.text.secondary },
});
```

For `StyleSheet.create` that needs theme values, create the stylesheet inside the component (or memoize with `useMemo`) so `theme` is in scope.

## Banned hex strings (old Midnight Edge)

Never introduce these values — they belong to the replaced theme:

`#0A0A0F` `#111118` `#1A1A24` `#131318` `#2A2A3A` `#4A4455`
`#7C3AED` `#D2BBFF` `#6D28D9` `#1F1F25` `#CCC3D8` `#FFB95F`

## Token quick-reference

Access all tokens via `const theme = useTheme();` → `theme.colors.<path>`.

### Backgrounds / depth

| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `depth.level0` | `#0D0D0D` | Deepest background, modals base |
| `depth.background` | `#111111` | Screen root `backgroundColor` |
| `depth.level1` | `#141414` | Cards, nav surface, bottom sheets |
| `depth.level2` | `#1C1C1C` | Elevated cards, input fields |

### Borders

| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `border.level1` | `#2E2E2E` | Default dividers and borders |

### Primary interactive

| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `primary.default` | `#F5F5F5` | Primary buttons, active highlights |
| `primary.dim` | `#B0B0B0` | Secondary buttons, ghost fills |
| `primary.active` | `#E0E0E0` | Pressed / active state |

### Text

| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `text.primary` | `#F5F5F5` | Headings, primary body |
| `text.secondary` | `#B0B0B0` | Subtitles, captions |
| `text.disabled` | `#3D3D3D` | Disabled labels |
| `text.onPrimary` | `#0D0D0D` | Text/icons **on** white primary buttons |

### Accent & gamification

| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `accent.amber` | `#D4AF37` | Premium CTAs, gold highlights |
| `gamification.emerald` | `#4EDEA3` | Success badges, streaks |

### Semantic

| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `semantic.success` | `#4EDEA3` | Success states |
| `semantic.warning` | `#D4AF37` | Warning states |
| `semantic.error` | `#F87171` | Error messages, destructive actions |

### Nav

| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `nav.surface` | `#141414` | Tab bar background |
| `nav.border` | `#2E2E2E` | Tab bar top border |
| `nav.inactive` | `#555555` | Unselected tab icons/labels |
| `nav.active` | `#F5F5F5` | Selected tab icon/label |

### Special effects

| Token | Value | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `focus.glow` | `rgba(245,245,245,0.15)` | Input focus ring shadow |
| `glass.border` | `rgba(245,245,245,0.08)` | Glassmorphism card border |
| `nav.surfaceScrim` | `rgba(20,20,20,0.92)` | Nav bar scrim overlay |
| `nav.iconGlow` | `rgba(245,245,245,0.2)` | Active tab icon glow |
| `gradient.premium` | `["#F5F5F5","#B0B0B0"]` | LinearGradient premium surfaces |

## Helper functions (from `src/config/theme.ts`)

```typescript
import { focusGlowStyle, navSurfaceStyle } from "@/config/theme";

// Focus ring on text inputs
const shadow = focusGlowStyle(theme); // returns shadowColor/Offset/Opacity/Radius

// Nav bar scrim
const scrim = navSurfaceStyle(theme); // returns backgroundColor
```

## `text.onPrimary` — semantic flip reminder

Primary is now **white** (`#F5F5F5`). Any text or icon that sits **on top of a primary-colored surface** must use `theme.colors.text.onPrimary` (`#0D0D0D`) — not white — so it remains legible.
